Crypt::Rot47 version 0.01
================================

This module applies the Rot47 substitution cipher on text, thereby scrambling the text and making it difficult for others to read. Applying the same Rot47 substitution cipher on the scrambled text well then restore the original text.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

Test::More

